itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"快啲罰"},{"pid":"9005b8a3c135d153725f317a1a1f8ccd05268ca4","tid":87357,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"總之佢邏輯就係人地去佢到，係佢比錢人賺<br />\n佢去人到都係佢比錢人䁠<br />\n點講都係佢益人"},{"pid":"903fcc70f47c62b05621d32ba93f3f6b429b232f","tid":87357,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c998a217bde2ff32ce5b974b11c7994193a02f2","tid":87357,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"若果侵侵話完全禁止支那人去美國，睇下篇文會點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13238c8c03fd454e527a9171c91a2e12a630cd4c","tid":87357,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}